{"tid":1590002,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中聯辦發表聲明嚴厲譴責極端激進分子近日多次肆意侮辱國旗","createTime":"2019-09-23T13:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T14:00:08.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c69ead0940534a9be53c1c810e9177a74dc0782d","tid":1590002,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:50:12.000Z","msg":"香港中聯辦發表聲明，嚴厲譴責極端激進分子，近日多次肆意侮辱國旗和連串違法暴力行徑。<br />\n<br />\n聲明表示，過去兩日，有極端激進分子在香港多個地區扯下國旗，肆意丟棄、燃燒，進行踐踏、侮辱。在近期的一些非法示威集會中，也多次發生極端激進分子侮辱國旗行為。負責人嚴正指出，這種嚴重違法行徑，是公然挑戰中央權威，褻瀆國家和民族尊嚴，踐踏「一國兩制」原則底線，極大地傷害了包括廣大香港同胞在內的全中國人民的感情，必須予以嚴厲譴責和依法懲治。<br />\n<br />\n負責人又表示，近日，一些目無法紀的暴徒持續將暴力升級，在香港多區堵路、縱火、破壞地鐵、圍攻特區政府官員、襲警和試圖搶奪警員佩槍，無差別殘暴毆打普通市民，這一系列帶有恐怖主義特徵的嚴重違法行為，已經突破了法律和道德的底線。負責人表示，堅決支持特區政府和警隊採取一切必要行動，嚴正果斷執法，儘快將暴徒繩之於法，止暴制亂，恢復秩序，共同捍衛法治公義和香港社會的安全穩定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482166-20190923.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482166-20190923.htm&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obugMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=9347e15a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482166-20190923.htm&h=e67c64ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482166-20190923.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f9d287af39be4c4afc59e041800adfc2a8ba55e7","tid":1590002,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802711615d3d5e48a47617c21f73304db759074c","tid":1590002,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"da9b8c562e89cb2d22f76fc4c93306532989dc8b","tid":1590002,"uid":302917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:51:44.000Z","msg":"中聯辦仲存在架？同王歧山鬥完未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a34f9e793107f1f3c2710fccac90cf7c1b63544","tid":1590002,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:58:36.000Z","msg":"好悶"},{"pid":"9054d71b992c370de5efbd93f772e8a7dc2a1541","tid":1590002,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:00:08.000Z","msg":"潛水潛咁耐先上番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}